## Change Hostname of Server

- Login to Plesk control panel
- Click on **Tools & Settings** from the left side menu

```diagram

```

- Under **General Settings** click on **Server Settings**

```diagram

```

- Write your new hosting in the **Full hostname** text box

```diagram

```

- Then click on OK

## Change System Time

- Login to Plesk control panel
- Click on **Tools & Settings** from the left side menu.
- Under **General Settings** click on **System Time**

```diagram

```

- Modify system time as per you need
